                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Unlike other rifle mods that affect status chance , Entropy Burst is an additive effect rather than a multiplicative one. This gives the Supra / Vandal , with its base status chance of 30%, a 50% Status Chance (30% + 20%), rather than 36 % (30% × (1 + 20%))."
